Package com.meterware.httpunit

Class BlockElement

java.lang.Object
com.meterware.httpunit.BlockElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
HTMLElement, HTMLSegment
Direct Known Subclasses:
TableCell, TextBlock
public abstract class BlockElement extends Object implements HTMLSegment, HTMLElement
Represents a block-level element such as a paragraph or table cell, which can contain other elements.
Since:
1.6
